OL,3,CRishi Sunak backs JK Rowling in row
OL,4,Cover Scotland's new hate crime laws
OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak has said
OL,7,F"nobody should be criminalised for
OL,8,Fsaying common sense things about
OL,9,Fbiological sex" after JK Rowling
OL,10,Fchallenged the Scottish Government's
OL,11,Fnew legislation.
OL,13,FThe Harry Potter author, who has
OL,14,Fbecome a fierce critic of the Scottish
OL,15,FGovernment's stance on transgender
OL,16,Frights, has been one of the highest
OL,17,Fprofile challengers of the legislation
OL,18,Fwhich she claims is "wide open to
OL,19,Fabuse."
