OL,3,CRishi Sunak backs JK Rowling in row
OL,4,Cover Scotland's new hate crime laws
OL,6,FThe Hate Crime and Public Order
OL,7,F(Scotland) Act came into effect on
OL,8,FMonday, consolidating existing hate
OL,9,Fcrime legislation and creating a new
OL,10,Foffence of stirring up hatred against
OL,11,Fprotected characteristics.
OL,13,FHowever, women have not been given
OL,14,Fprotection under the law, with the
OL,15,FScottish Government instead promising
OL,16,Fto bring forward legislation to tackle
OL,17,Fmisogyny.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/17
