OL,3,CRishi Sunak backs JK Rowling in row
OL,4,Cover Scotland's new hate crime laws
OL,6,FBut with the new Act giving protection
OL,7,Fto transgender people, Rowling, who
OL,8,Fdoes not believe people can change
OL,9,Ftheir gender, insisted: "Freedom of
OL,10,Fspeech and belief are at an end in
OL,11,FScotland if the accurate description
OL,12,Fof biological sex is deemed criminal."
OL,14,FThe prime minister appeared to back
OL,15,Fthe author's criticism and said there
OL,16,Fare no plans "to do anything like that
OL,17,Fhere in England".
