OL,3,CRishi Sunak backs JK Rowling in row
OL,4,Cover Scotland's new hate crime laws
OL,6,F"We should not be criminalising people
OL,7,Fsaying common sense things about
OL,8,Fbiological sex - clearly that isn't
OL,9,Fright," he told broadcasters on
OL,10,FTuesday.
OL,12,F"We have a proud tradition of free
OL,13,Fspeech and I think it just shows -
OL,14,Fwhether it's the SNP or Labour - these
OL,15,Fare the wrong set of priorities for
OL,16,Fthe country."
