OL,3,CRishi Sunak backs JK Rowling in row
OL,4,Cover Scotland's new hate crime laws
OL,6,FWhen pressed if he supports Rowling's
OL,7,Fapproach, Mr Sunak replied: "It's not
OL,8,Fright for me to comment on police
OL,9,Fmatters, individual matters, but what
OL,10,FI do support very strongly are
OL,11,Fpeople's right to free speech" but
OL,12,Fadded that "nobody should be
OL,13,Fcriminalised for saying common sense
OL,14,Fthings about biological sex".
