OL,6,FRowling added: "I'm currently out of
OL,7,Fthe country, but if what I've written
OL,8,Fhere qualifies as an offence under the
OL,9,Fterms of the new act, I look forward
OL,10,Fto being arrested when I return to the
OL,11,Fbirthplace of the Scottish
OL,12,FEnlightenment."
OL,14,FThe legislation consolidates existing
OL,15,Fhate crime laws and creates a new
