OL,3,CRishi Sunak backs JK Rowling in row
OL,4,Cover Scotland's new hate crime laws
OL,6,FIn a letter to Holyrood's Justice
OL,7,FCommittee, they said the law could be
OL,8,F"weaponised" by an "activist fringe"
OL,9,Facross the political spectrum.
OL,11,FBut on Friday, First Minister Humza
OL,12,FYousaf said: "I would say to anybody
OL,13,Fwho thinks they are a victim of
OL,14,Fhatred, we take that seriously, if you
OL,15,Ffelt you are a victim of hatred, then
OL,16,Fof course reporting that to police is
OL,17,Fthe right thing to do.
