OL,6,FBut Police Scotland Chief Constable Jo
OL,7,FFarrell, speaking at a meeting of the
OL,8,FScottish Police Authority board, said
OL,9,Fthe force would apply the Act "in a
OL,10,Fmeasured way".
OL,12,FShe added that there would be "close
OL,13,Fscrutiny" of how the legislation is
OL,14,Fbeing enforced as well as what reports
OL,15,Fare being received.
OL,17,FThe law coming into force comes as
OL,18,FTory MSP Murdo Fraser revealed Police
OL,19,FScotland had recorded a non-crime hate
OL,20,Fincident in relation to a social media
OL,21,Fpost he made last year.
